      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA HANDLE IT (2) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including three wins. Recorded a half a length win (29.93) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Looks a key chance on best form. STILTON SHINE (6) is worth forgiving for her last effort when sixth (30.27) at this track over 520m. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Cannot be taken lightly. OCCULENT (3) is a well performed dog and winner of seven races who was in the minor money last time out at this track (29.97). Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expected to feature again. HEY BUBBA LOUIE (7) is a last-start placegetter and was in front for a fair way - in the mix again.",
